Meet-A-Rep Social Event

This Wednesday, join us for cocktails at a nearby restaurant, and meet a few of our New Hampshire State Reps! All friends of liberty are welcome to stop by. There will be a cover charge of $5 for appetizers, plus a cash bar.

The event will be on Wednesday, January 21, from 4 to 6 pm, at the Concord Grille (previously known as the Capitol Grille) at 1 Eagle Square in Concord. Please RSVP to chair@nhliberty.org to ensure that we have enough food for everyone.

I hope youâ€™ll join us! This is a great opportunity to support the efforts of the NHLA and to show the reps the caliber of liberty activists we have in the area.



Mark Warden
